parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
injuries or fatalities occurred
airbag warning light illuminated on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The recall of Takata airbags has left many vehicles without a functional airbag system, putting occupants at risk of serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Receipt of recall notification
inability to obtain replacement parts
delay in repair
concern about airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A melting or cracking dashboard can cause the airbag to deploy improperly or not at all, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Dashboard is melting or cracking
airbag is compromised
concern about airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the low beam headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Low beam headlights do not turn on
intermittently go out
or burn out frequently
requiring repeated replacements. In some cases
the headlights may only work when the high beams are engaged or when the headlight assembly is tapped or hit.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gas Tank Leaking and Fuel Fumes
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A leaking gas tank can cause fuel fumes to enter the vehicle, posing a fire hazard and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Strong gas fumes are present after filling the gas tank
and gas leaks are observed at half or full tank levels
both when the vehicle is stationary and in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the headlights, taillights, and dash lights to malfunction or shut down, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: Headlights
taillights
or dash lights suddenly shut down or malfunction
melting wires
burning out bulbs
or causing electrical shorts; door open icon illuminates despite all doors being closed; vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, especially at night, leading to increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights burn out or malfunction
requiring frequent replacement; headlights shut down suddenly
especially on low beam; headlights can be temporarily restored by bumping the headlight assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle can cause loss of control, especially at high speeds, leading to increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
often requiring restart; vehicle may experience electrical system malfunctions or warning lights prior to stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting or deterioration of the dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, obstructing the driver's view and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard is sticky
cracked
or broken
with pieces falling off; a glare on the windshield affects visibility while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sun/moonroof can cause broken glass to fall, posing a risk to the occupants' safety and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The sun/moonroof suddenly shatters or explodes
with no warning messages or lights indicating the failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the rear subframe can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, affecting its safety and performance.
symptoms: The rear subframe is rusted in layers
with spalling or flaking off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unidentified grinding sound can be a sign of a underlying issue that may affect the vehicle's performance and safety.
symptoms: A grinding sound occurs when the car starts after standing for a couple of days; the issue remains unfixed despite multiple attempts.
